                    "body": "I have some issues with the way that this has been implemented, the partial class is being used to set parameters in the view that are created in the partialLoop extension of the class. I have a working copy of my own version of partialLoop that does not require changes to partial to make it work.\r\n\r\nBittarman has kindly offered to mentor me next week so that I can figure out how to get my proposed changes into the system for review.\r\n\r\nJust wanted to make a note of my intentions incase anyone here already has some other ideas - and so I don't forget, or get lazy and not do it ;-)\r\n\r\n",
